== Additional Notes == * Due to the {{ill|2011 Tōhoku earthquake and tsunami|ja|東日本大震災|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the festival in 2011 was limited to mikoshi rituals, with taiko performances and food stalls canceled. * In 2023, to prevent the involvement of {{ill|yakuza|ja|暴力団|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, stall owners and workers were required to display photo IDs.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yomiuri.co.jp/national/20230611-OYT1T50131/2/ |title=Preventing Organized Crime at Festivals: Yomiuri Shimbun |publisher=Yomiuri Shimbun |date=June 11, 2023 |accessdate=June 12, 2023}}</ref>
